---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';
---

<Layout title="Migrating from Wix to AI Builders: How to Switch">
  <StructuredData type="WebPage" data={{ name: 'Migrating from Wix to AI Builders Guide', description: 'Step-by-step guide to migrate from Wix to AI website builders. Export content, redirect URLs, minimize SEO impact.', url: 'https://aiwebsitebuilders.com/guides/migrating-from-wix-to-ai-builders' }} />

  <section class="bg-[#FFF8F0] py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">Migrating from Wix:<span class="block text-[#F5521A]">The Complete Guide</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mt-6">Leave Wix without killing your SEO. Step-by-step migration process.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">The Bad News First</h2>
      <div class="bg-red-50 border-[3px] border-red-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-red-800">⚠️ Wix doesn't let you export your site.</p>
        <p class="text-sm mt-2">There's NO way to download your Wix site and move it elsewhere. You have to rebuild.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Migration Process</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3">Step 1: Audit Your Content</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• List all pages (10-50 typically)</li>
            <li>• Export all images and media</li>
            <li>• Copy all text content to docs</li>
            <li>• Note SEO meta titles/descriptions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3">Step 2: Choose New Builder</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Portfolios → Framer (9.2/10)</li>
            <li>• E-commerce → 10Web (8.8/10)</li>
            <li>• Simple sites → Durable (8.5/10)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3">Step 3: Build New Site</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Use AI generator to recreate layout</li>
            <li>• Manually copy-paste your content</li>
            <li>• Re-upload images</li>
            <li>• Set up pages and navigation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-5 rounded-xl">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3">Step 4: Redirect URLs</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>• Keep Wix site live temporarily</li>
            <li>• Set up 301 redirects from old to new URLs</li>
            <li>• Update domain DNS to new builder</li>
            <li>• Cancel Wix after 30 days</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Best Alternatives to Wix</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl border-[3px] border-gray-200">
          <thead class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
            <tr><th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-bold">Use Case</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Switch To</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Why</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Portfolio</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-[#F5521A]">Framer</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm">Better design, cheaper</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">E-commerce</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-[#F5521A]">10Web</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm">WooCommerce power, cheaper</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Simple site</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-[#F5521A]">Durable</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-sm">Faster, simpler</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">SEO Survival Tips</h2>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-[3px] border-green-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>✓ Keep identical URL structure if possible</li>
          <li>✓ Match meta titles and descriptions exactly</li>
          <li>✓ Set up 301 redirects (Google uses these to transfer ranking)</li>
          <li>✓ Submit new sitemap to Google Search Console</li>
          <li>✓ Expect ranking dip for 2-4 weeks, then recovery</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
